## 4. Folder Design & Structure

```
alg-discovery/
├── .cursor/rules/          # Cursor rules (project-master, etc.)
├── frontend/
│   ├── docs/               # All frontend docs (no loose .md in root)
│   │   ├── README.md        # Index
│   │   ├── environment.md
│   │   └── deployment.md
│   ├── envs/               # env.dev, env.stage, env.prod
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── components/     # Reusable UI components
│   │   ├── config/         # API config (no duplicate config files)
│   │   ├── hooks/
│   │   ├── pages/
│   │   ├── services/       # One concern per file, no duplicates
│   │   └── types/
│   └── public/
├── scripts/                # Deploy, CI scripts
└── docs/                   # Repo-level deployment docs
```

- **Docs**: All frontend docs in `frontend/docs/`. No loose `.md` files in frontend root.
- **Config**: Use env files and config modules; no hardcoded values. No duplicate config files.
- **Services**: One concern per file. Scan for similar logic; consolidate, don't duplicate.

